    <lb n="2"/>Κτησικλῆς πρὸς Διονύσιον καὶ 

    <lb n="3"/>Νίκην τὴν θυγατέρα περὶ <expan>χειρογρ<ex cert="high">αφίας</ex></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-221" notBefore="-221" type="textDate" value="-0221-02-27">27. Febr. 221 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 5: <date notAfter="-0229" notBefore="-0230" type="mentioned">230 - 229 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Enteux.</title><biblScope type="numbers">26</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">3301</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0106</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">26</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0106;;26" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">119</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Sel. Pap. II 268</bibl></div><div n="meta.3301" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations">TUAT, N.F. 3 (2006), VIII 7.1.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Bagnall &amp; Derow, The Hellenistic Period (2004), Nr. 152</bibl></list